---
title: Mediterranean Tomato, Bacon & Silverbeet Risotto with Parmesan & Roasted Almonds
description: Satisfy your tastebuds with an expertly cooked and flavoured risotto (in case it wasn’t clear, you’re the expert!). Hearty and
homey, this warming bowl incorporates caramelised cherry tomatoes, bacon and silverbeet to create a risotto that has everyone
humming from bliss.
